---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience | Joydip Dutta">
  <section class="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 mb-24 max-w-2xl duration-700 ease-out">
    <h1 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter md:text-5xl">
      Experience_Log
    </h1>
    <p class="text-muted inline-block rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-4 font-mono">
      <span class="text-accent">~ $ grep "Software Development Engineer" system.log</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="relative ml-3 border-l border-zinc-800 pb-12 md:ml-4">
    <!-- Timeline Item 1 -->
    <div class="relative mb-16 pl-8 md:pl-10">
      <span
        class="bg-accent ring-background absolute top-1.5 -left-1.25 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full ring-4"
      ></span>

      <div class="mb-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-foreground text-xl font-bold">Software Development Engineer</h3>
        <span class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-500 md:mt-0">Jan 2026 – Present</span>
      </div>

      <h4 class="text-accent mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm">
        @ Gunpowder Innovations
        <span class="text-zinc-600">| London, UK - Remote</span>
      </h4>

      <ul class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-3">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Zero-Trust Data Security:</strong> Architected a robust Row-Level Security (ACL)
            system across 61 Prisma models for a multi-tenant platform, utilizing Redis-backed caching
            and specific handlers to enforce strict data isolation.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-3">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Financial Orchestration:</strong> Integrated external financial APIs (WealthKernel
            and Plaid) and managed a reliable, event-driven webhook pipeline that processes 31 different
            event types via BullMQ with secure signature verification.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-3">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Banking-Grade Encryption:</strong> Implemented AES-256-GCM field-level encryption
            with zero-downtime key rotation to protect sensitive user data, ensuring strict financial
            compliance while maintaining exceptionally low query latency.</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
    <div class="relative mb-16 pl-8 md:pl-10">
      <span
        class="ring-background absolute top-1.5 -left-1.25 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 ring-4"
      ></span>

      <div class="mb-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-foreground text-xl font-bold">Software Development Engineer</h3>
        <span class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-500 md:mt-0">Jan 2023 – Dec 2025</span>
      </div>

      <h4 class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-400">
        @ The Internet Folks
        <span class="text-zinc-600">| Bhopal, MP - Remote</span>
      </h4>

      <ul class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>High-Scale Architecture:</strong> Maintained highly reliable backend services for
            over 30,000 users, utilizing dynamic database partitioning in MongoDB to manage millions of
            records safely.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Polyglot Microservices:</strong> Architected a flexible, multi-language backend system
            using TypeScript and Go, smartly directing heavy tracking data to ClickHouse and core relational
            data to PostgreSQL for maximum performance.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Enterprise AI Integration:</strong> Developed a hybrid AI system combining semantic
            search (pgvector) with multi-LLM generation (OpenAI, Gemini), allowing enterprise clients
            to securely plug in their own AI keys (BYOK).</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Automated Financial Ledgers (FaaS):</strong> Created a multi-tenant "Fund as a Service"
            platform using PostgreSQL and Drizzle ORM, designing a strict financial ledger that accurately
            tracks capital flows and fees.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Digital Agriculture (AgriEasy):</strong> Built a digital agriculture platform featuring
            a real-time negotiation engine, enabling farmers to agree on contracts and automatically generating
            personalized, day-by-day crop care schedules.</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
    <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-10">
      <span
        class="ring-background absolute top-1.5 -left-1.25 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 ring-4"
      ></span>

      <div class="mb-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-foreground text-xl font-bold">Software Development Intern</h3>
        <span class="mt-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-500 md:mt-0">June 2022 – Aug 2022</span>
      </div>

      <h4 class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-400">
        @ AUM Capital Market Private Limited
        <span class="text-zinc-600">| Kolkata, WB</span>
      </h4>

      <ul class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            ><strong>Process Automation:</strong> Developed a React and Node.js solution to automate government
            bond calculations and payment reminders, cutting down manual administrative work by approximately
            80%.</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
